channel.title: How do I delete things
channel.description:
How would I go about removing things? I would love to remove everything and build my own Runescape, just like that guy's alienscape. It looks amazing, how would I go about editing things like that.
Also if anyone knew how I could edit colors and edit names of items, that would be great.
Perhaps I was a bit vague when I said things. I mean buildings.
